        <title>linux下man手册的安装和使用</title>
        <link>https://ynhugo.github.io/p/linux%E4%B8%8Bman%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</link>
